      <Item ItemId=";debug.warningMessage" ItemType="0" PsrId="306" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[To debug applications in Teams, your localhost server need to be on HTTPS.]A;For Teams to trust the self-signed SSL certificate used by the toolkit, add a self-signed certificate to your certificate store.]A; You may skip this step, but you'll have to manually trust the secure connection in a new browser window when debugging your apps in Teams.]A;For more information "https://aka.ms/teamsfx-ca-certificate".]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[Pokud chcete ladit aplikace v Teams, musí být váš server localhost na adrese HTTPS.]A;Aby mohl Teams důvěřovat certifikátu SSL podepsanému jeho držitelem, který používá sada nástrojů, přidejte si tento certifikát do úložiště certifikátů.]A; Tento krok můžete přeskočit, ale při ladění aplikací v Teams v novém okně prohlížeče budete muset zabezpečené připojení ručně nastavit jako důvěryhodné.]A;Další informace najdete na adrese https://aka.ms/teamsfx-ca-certificate.]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
          <Prev Cat="Text">
            <Val><![CDATA[To debug applications in Teams, your localhost server must be on HTTPS.]A;For Teams to trust the self-signed SSL certificate used by the toolkit, a self-signed certificate must be added to your certificate store.]A; You may skip this step, but you'll have to manually trust the secure connection in a new browser window when debugging your apps in Teams.]A;For more information "https://aka.ms/teamsfx-ca-certificate".]]></Val>
          </Prev>
        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
      <Item ItemId=";debug.warningMessage2" ItemType="0" PsrId="306" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[ You may be asked for your account credentials when installing the certificate.]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
