          </Tgt>
          <Prev Cat="Text">
            <Val><![CDATA[Unable to update or delete an existing permission when it's enabled. One possible reason is that the ACCESS_AS_USER_PERMISSION_ID environment variable is changed for selected environment. Ensure your permission id(s) are identical with the actual AAD application and try again.]A;]]></Val>
